PGM Map Collection
A collection of publicly downloadable Minecraft maps made for PGM

This collection of maps have been specifically designed and tested to be used with the maintained PGMDev version of PGM (Pvp Game Manager). ResourcePile recommends that you use the most up-to-date version of this PGM in order to have the best experience with this map. To setup your own PGM server, please follow this guide. Further PGM support can be found in the PGM Discord.

Filters Use filters to narrow your query when searching for specific maps.
